title: Frank Lloyd Wright Window from the Coonley Playhouse, Riverside, Illinois Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from Frank Lloyd Wright’s Window from the Coonley Playhouse, Riverside, Illinois, 1912, from The Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet.
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 2.5 in.
